directions: Combine salad, oranges, fennel and olives in large bowl. Toss with Fresh Orange Dressing, to coat, as desired. Refrigerate any remaining vinaigrette.
ingredients: 1 (6 ounce) package DOLE® Tender Garden Blend
2 oranges, peeled and cut in half slices
1 fennel bulb, trimmed, cored and thinly sliced lengthwise
8 pitted Kalamata olives, cut in half
title: Orange and Fennel Salad
